    nslookup &lt;server&gt;.&lt;expected domain&gt;

you may get:

    Non-authoritative answer:
    Name:   &lt;server&gt;.&lt;expected domain, for instance your company&#39;s domain&gt;
    Address: &lt;IP&gt;

